          <p class="feature-description">
            Plan and track your workouts with our intuitive calendar system.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Nutrition Planning</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">
            Access detailed meal plans and nutritional guidance from certified
            experts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M17 10.5V7c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H4c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v10c0 .55.45 1 1 1h12c.55 0 1-.45 1-1v-3.5l4 4v-11l-4 4zM14 13h-3v3H9v-3H6v-2h3V8h2v3h3v2z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Video Library</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">
            Stream high-quality workout videos from professional trainers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M19 3h-4.18C14.4 1.84 13.3 1 12 1c-1.3 0-2.4.84-2.82 2H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 0c.55 0 1 .45 1 1s-.45 1-1 1-1-.45-1-1 .45-1 1-1zm0 4c1.66 0 3 1.34 3 3s-1.34 3-3 3-3-1.34-3-3 1.34-3 3-3zm6 12H6v-1.4c0-2 4-3.1 6-3.1s6 1.1 6 3.1V19z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Health Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">
            Get personalized lab test recommendations and health insights.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-5 14H7v-2h7v2zm3-4H7v-2h10v2zm0-4H7V7h10v2z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Expert Content</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">
            Read articles and guides from fitness professionals and health
            experts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Add this section before the questions-section -->
    <section class="testimonials" id="success-stories">
      <h2>Success Stories</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Real transformations from our community members</p>

      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-image">
            <img
              src="/male-body-transformation-london-1-1.webp"
              alt="Transformation"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <div class="quote">
              "RevibeFit changed my life! Lost 25kgs in 6 months with
              personalized training and <br />following the Zumba Classes"
            </div>
            <div class="author">
              <strong>Sarah Mitchell</strong>
              <span>Lost 25 KG</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-image">
            <img src="/journey.png" alt="Transformation" />
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <div class="quote">
              "The trainers here are exceptional. Achieved my fitness goals in
              just 4 months!"
            </div>
            <div class="author">
              <strong>John Davis</strong>
              <span>Gained Muscle Mass</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-image">
            <img src="/shutterstock_1240081561.webp" alt="Transformation" />
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <div class="quote">
              "Perfect blend of nutrition and workout guidance. My diabetes is
              now under control."
            </div>
            <div class="author">
              <strong>Mike Wilson</strong>
              <span>Health Transformation</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="questions-section">
      <h2>Still have questions?</h2>
      <p>Please help us understand your doubts and we'll get back to you</p>
      <a href="contact_us.html" class="contact-button">Contact Us</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <div id="footer"></div>
    </footer>
    <script>
      $(function () {
        $("#nav-placeholder").load("Nav_bar.html");
      });
      fetch("footer.html")
        .then((response) => response.text())
        .then((data) => (document.getElementById("footer").innerHTML = data));
    </script>
